    answer: "Crazy Crosswords is free to download and play. Optional in-app purchases are available for hints and additional puzzle packs."
  },
  {
    question: "How often are new puzzles added?",
    answer: "We add new puzzle packs regularly through updates. Each pack contains dozens of unique challenges to keep your mind sharp."
